{
  "stem": "3097.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In fact, some people tried to escape from Blizyn to come to us, and from Pionki also to come to us.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because was-- by us, was a little but not so bad here.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because I think that the-- the director of the factories, Mr.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Hirsch-- ?] he was an SA member.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was one of the SS.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But he was not very strict.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And our Henrykow, you see, we had a fellow by the name Fuss, was very, very bad.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "F-U-S-S.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Fuss, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] we-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] they took us over there, under guard, and we walked.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We walked to [?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Ludvikow ?] originally, OK?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because Henrykow was not ready yet, the barracks.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I don't-- maybe 4 miles.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's all.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when they made a camp for us in Henrykow they transferred me and Wasser to Henrykow Minsberg and Mosberg stayed in [?",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Ludvikow, ?] OK?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And Wasser-- we used to have the same bunk, and so forth, you see.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Our barrack mainly was a horse stable with small windows on the top.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was a big, big, long barrack.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the roof was made out of tin.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So in-- in summer, it was very, very hot.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "In fact, I was assigned-- we had two people to one bunk, me and Wasser.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I was assigned to sleep with him on the bottom.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And fleas were jumping and bite us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I gave a piece of bread and so forth, a piece of sausage, I think I gave, and he gave something.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We bribed ourselves to get on the top.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But it was bad, because the sun then hit the roof and was so hot.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But we didn't have a chance, except when we worked night shift.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
